data.description: Tucked away on a serene cul-de-sac, this 4-bed, 2-bath energy-efficient home with solar panels, an RV gate, and a tasteful desert landscape. The interior welcomes you with a soothing palette and tile flooring in the living room, while the family room features recessed lighting, backyard access, and a cozy fireplace. The eat-in kitchen boasts another inviting fireplace, SS appliances, paneled cabinets, a convenient serving window, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. The main bedroom provides a tranquil escape with a private bathroom, ensuring comfort and convenience. The sprawling backyard is a true oasis, featuring a covered patio for al fresco dining. New ROOF, AC and water heater! Loan is assumable at 2.99% Interest Rate! Call Listing Agent for details on Assumable Loan Process!
